name: The Sound Of Memories Flying Away
description:
The sky won’t let me fly
The earth won’t let me walk on it nor will it swallow me.
The sea won’t let me drown.
Death won’t take me.
Love refused me.
Life has turned its back to me.
What am I to do?
Here as the torch is lighted, the flame
of dreams to reach the sky is ignited.
And these dreams will continue to linger long.
